\subtree{
\title{GF(3) Conservation}
\p{At every level, the sum of trits = 0:}

\pre{\startverb
| Property | Count | Value |
|----------|-------|-------|
| MINUS leaves | 9 | -9 |
| MIDDLE leaves | 9 | 0 |
| PLUS leaves | 9 | +9 |
| **Sum** | 27 | **0 ✓** |
\stopverb}
}

